data.description: A combination of athletic movements such as running, jumping, and lunging, combined with squats and push-ups. This class involves building your stamina, coordination and agility, making you fitter. You will also build speed with the sports inspired moves, meaning you'll be quicker with everything. This is also a great class for those wishing to increase their cardio. The instructor will challenge your limits, you'll be left with an amazing sense of achievement and you'll quickly burn calories while toning and shaping your whole body. This is a great class if you want to increase your functional fitness and cardio. BODYATTACK is suitable for all ages and abilities. For the best results take a class two to three times a week.

data.description: A class that will improve not just your body but also your mind. Bend and stretch through movements that combine the best of yoga, Tai Chi and Pilates, while listening to an inspiring soundtrack. This holistic workout is a brilliant way to find harmony and balance. An important part of this class is learning breathing control, and our instructors will help you learn this, with options for those just getting started. You'll experience increased core strength, less stress and a feeling of wellbeing and happiness. Our instructors will also help you strengthen your whole body and you'll leave feeling calm and strong. BODYBALANCE is suitable for beginners and those more experienced at yoga. To feel the benefits we recommend you attend a class at least once a week.

data.description: A class that will improve not just your body but also your mind. Bend and stretch through movements that combine the best of yoga, Tai Chi and Pilates, while listening to an inspiring soundtrack. This holistic workout is a brilliant way to find harmony and balance. An important part of this class is learning breathing control, and our instructors will help you learn this, with options for those just getting started. You'll experience increased core strength, less stress and a feeling of wellbeing and happiness. Our instructors will also help you strengthen your whole body and you'll leave feeling calm and strong. BODYBALANCE is suitable for beginners and those more experienced at yoga. To feel the benefits we recommend you attend a class at least once a week.
